{"tid":1006465,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖兩年　林秀怡儲錢押後婚期","createTime":"2019-02-03T04:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T10:42:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04ad02771b497462b06d9f797fdb1f1e636936a3","tid":1006465,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190131000346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190131000346&h=170eed30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_03b.jpg?20190131000346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20190131000346&h=962b8817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_04b.jpg?20190131000346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20190131000346&h=a733bf60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_05b.jpg?20190131000346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20190131000346&h=2616da47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_06b.jpg?20190131000346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20190131000346&h=7e08736f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n憑無綫劇《是咁的，法官閣下》為人熟悉的林秀怡（Kirby），去年大方承認戀上導演男友，在她眼中對方好靚仔，認真工作時夠晒型，更直認嫁得過！Kirby為東網巨星節目「海馬牌床褥特約」《閨蜜睡房》擔任最新一集嘉賓，與主持人李惠儀暢談其事業和愛情。Kirby說：「喺學校我係活躍分子，一直有參加戲劇學會、合唱團，總之坐唔定嘅活動啱晒我，雖然做藝人收入唔穩定，都有氣餒過，但呢個諗法最多一個鐘，其實可以將自己嘅興趣變做工作，我覺得好幸福。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>老夫老妻冇驚喜</strong><br />\n<br />\n談起因合作而認識的導演男友，Kirby毫不扭擰，笑着讚對方靚仔，她說：「佢叫我幫手去台灣拍微電影，我咪應承，當見到佢拍嘢時好認真，覺得佢好有型、好吸引。」他們拍拖近兩年，已有老夫老妻感覺：「我哋拍拖嘅日子好平淡，我同佢都唔係點識製造驚喜，平日都係行街、睇戲、食飯。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不受年齡局限</strong><br />\n<br />\n今年27歲的她曾想30歲前出嫁，但笑言要押後到35歲，因早前她為母親醫病花了大筆錢：「我都係體諒佢，都要畀時間佢儲吓錢，費事畀年齡限住自己。」想知道她為男友做過最浪漫的事？以及兩人拍拖趣事，記得本星期五、六、日收睇《閨蜜睡房》！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190131/bkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190131%2Fbkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001.html&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7qZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=b239ec01\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190131/bkn-20190131000037029-0131_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"beb7beba01d051e31512ab8b32010a4c4dd91e7b","tid":1006465,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"Who.jpg"},{"pid":"008a06f0930cccdbd1303d5a169aab977acb33a2","tid":1006465,"uid":57776,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"Who"},{"pid":"07ddf796388994fcd17b8babd7301c33f6b56123","tid":1006465,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"888d4d8003196142eed8827ea83095bb51a5391f","tid":1006465,"uid":20653,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 上面成班連水野朝陽都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e0c2fb2a31971033ef55d2bd4bf9c76fc4cc4f","tid":1006465,"uid":34935,"li